com.rexsl.maven.packers

Class PackersProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rexsl.maven.packers.PackersProvider

  • public final class PackersProvider
extends Object
    Provider of a collection of all packers.

    Packers are executed in the order they are listed here.

    CssPacker

    All files from src/main/webapp/css (CSS stylesheets) are compressed using YUI compressor. Then, they are saved to target/../css.

    JsPacker

    All files from src/main/webapp/js (JavaScript files) are compressed using YUI compressor. Then, they are saved to target/../js.

    XslPacker

    All files from src/main/webapp/xsl (XSL stylesheets) are compressed as XML documents and all comments are removed. Then, they are saved to target/../xsl.

    Version:
    $Id$
